explanation: [0-0] The video starts with a hand holding a bottle of black nail polish. On the left side, there is a TikTok logo and white English text.

[0-10] Then, a person dips a brush into the nail polish and applies the black polish to a transparent fake nail. The scene then switches to a container with a green grid pattern, around which there is some residual green pigment. Using tweezers, the green grid pattern is placed onto the fake nail coated with black nail polish, and a wooden stick is used to flatten the green grid pattern, making it adhere to the fake nail. Afterward, some transparent viscous liquid is placed on the nail with a metal tool and then spread evenly with a brush. Immediately, a pair of tweezers is used to hold a transparent film, which is then placed on the fake nail and pressed down with a white tool. Finally, the film is peeled off, revealing the completed fake nail with the green grid pattern. On the right side, the white English text "ilysmnails.com" appears.
